title.narrative: Lao PDR: Support for Clearance of Unexploded Ordnance (UXO)

description.narrative: This activity supports the clearance of unexploded ordinance (UXO) and cluster munitions from rural land to ensure safe use of UXO-contaminated land in Lao PDR’s Xieng Khouang Province for socio-economic, humanitarian and disaster risk reduction purposes.
